         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Christian symbol). To my lord and beloved father Phamaeis, Bes the wine merchant, greeting. Before all else I greet repeatedly you and my mother Thermouthis and your household Ç«Ù may the evil eye not touch them Ç«Ù each by name. You did well to send me . . .;;(Verso) . . . to my lord . . . .</ab>
         </div>
